Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个……谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉 支援我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是导师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然无效吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非无效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是它的污秽太强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人看不下去 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子就是新的导师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是你干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭魔由我来送下地狱 这就是我的做派
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拥有能够消灭凭魔的特殊道具与道具要使用的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意儿是特制的 是我特别特别重要的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把杀害当成做派……？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还有可以不取性命就能救它的方法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪个时代的导师都是一群好学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 导师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也说不定……有的人是只有杀了他才算是救他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该跟你说过别再来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也应该跟你说过 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次我都会来 直到杀了他为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就……别再管我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是领域？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么充满污秽的……是领域？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道……怎么会……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这条龙就是艾德娜的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个！不想被吃掉的话就快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉！我们赶快「神依」！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是天族的话 就用净化的力量来……！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实体化的龙是没法净化的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那……艾德娜的哥哥不就……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远……都是这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的……没有办法能解决吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法我去找过 然而无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 所以我得亲手 送他下地狱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别管我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！这里太危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧带艾德娜跑远点儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有净化的力量还是没法打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 在这种地方……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷不能没我陪着……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 他好像飞远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算抓我的手抓到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是乎 你们的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是依循龙的传说来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要屠龙剑圣的称号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是在瑞迪雷克有龙出现……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都有龙？那不是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你来干嘛的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个被称作「灾厄的时代」的世界是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说龙是毁灭的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那追寻龙的踪迹 说不定就能更了解世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为了导师 所以……必须要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那你现在知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙到底是个什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再待在这里也是白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以赶紧回……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 关于龙我已经清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在想 要救龙……要救艾森应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉 这小子是不是傻？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷的优点就是特别直率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 艾森为什么会变成龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不说一声就离开 再见到就已经变成龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个很喜欢人类的怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是因为他跟人走得太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在寻找让哥哥恢复原样的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿都没有能净化龙的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……你并不希望他被杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你也想阻止扎比达来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前一直以为导师和龙都是传说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界上还有好多没有被揭开过的传说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会有拯救龙的方法……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森……扎比达……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 不许再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙已经不是艾森了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都不知道站在那边的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经忘记一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了我们之前打过多少次架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了他曾经拼上性命旅行过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了跟我一起喝到酩酊大醉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些你全都……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉 请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙是无法净化的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我……想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我必须去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷 已经……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没……我还能……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再伤害别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 快离开那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥……哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾森 你……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达 那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 你想说艾森是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟看见了那一幕……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比达……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也满世界转过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从来没听说过龙能恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 世界那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没准……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找找也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜 你什么时候打算放弃他 随时来跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会立刻飞奔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟早就跟他约好了……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算有一个笨蛋走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉 麻烦你进行陪神契约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾多娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是遵循古时的契约 我借给你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要救艾森 所以我要帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是答应要帮我找拯救哥哥的办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 肯定帮你 我们一起找！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教了 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请你多指教 艾德娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着 史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里弗雷特桥被……
